summary: Iron Man 2
title: Iron Man 2
body:
Hello one and all to another Live Blog by me, The Nerd Wonder. Today we’re watching Iron Man 2. This was the movie that I think really got me into the MCU. Of course I’d seen Iron Man 1–rather important to see 1 when watching 2–but that was just another good action movie. So as good as IM is, that could’ve been a fluke. I didn’t know about the end credits scenes yet, so I didn’t know that they were planning a whole franchise yet. But here, with Black Widow and Fury and Coulson taking a larger role, I could see that they were planning something. Whatever this “Avengers” thing was, I was intrigued. 

Yes, I know many people hate this movie. And maybe looking at it with a critical eye rather than “Let’s just watch this random action movie while chowing down on pizza, fam” I might like it less too. But it’s still the movie that made me start to believe in the MCU, and that’s something special. Without further ado: ROLL IT!
